<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{أَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ لِدُلُوكِ الشَّمْسِ إِلَى غَسَقِ اللَّيْلِ , وَقُرْآنَ الْفَجْرِ , إِنَّ قُرْآنَ الْفَجْرِ كَانَ مَشْهُودًا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٨٦:</span> <span class="c3">{وَقُرْآنَ الْفَجْرِ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: <span class="c1">" صَلَاةَ الفَجْرِ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
